articles.title: Phillies add All-Star Soto in 5-player trade with Tigers
articles.description: PHILADELPHIA -- The Phillies continued to bolster their bullpen on Saturday, acquiring two-time All-Star Gregory Soto from the Tigers in a five-player deal.
